  <sec id="ai-usage-disclosure">
    <title>AI usage disclosure</title>
    <p>As described in-repo, AI providers used with constrained tasks
    and strict human review:</p>
    <list list-type="bullet">
      <list-item>
        <p>Claude
        (<xref alt="Anthropic, 2025" rid="ref-claude_ai" ref-type="bibr">Anthropic,
