        (<xref alt="GitHub et al., 2025" rid="ref-copilot" ref-type="bibr">GitHub
        et al., 2025</xref>)</p>
      </list-item>
      <list-item>
        <p>IntelliJ
        (<xref alt="Sokolov, 2024" rid="ref-intellij_ai" ref-type="bibr">Sokolov,
        2024</xref>)</p>
      </list-item>
      <list-item>
        <p>Replit
        (<xref alt="Replit, 2025" rid="ref-replit_ai" ref-type="bibr">Replit,
        2025</xref>).</p>
      </list-item>
    </list>
    <p>No substantial LLM use in original JavaScript implementation.</p>
